```plantuml
@startuml freenowtech_AndroidCI

actor Developer

participant Jenkins
participant Docker
participant AndroidSDK

Developer -> Jenkins: Trigger Build
Jenkins -> Docker: Start Build Container
Docker -> AndroidSDK: Access SDK
AndroidSDK -> Docker: Provide Build Tools
Docker -> Jenkins: Execute Build
Docker -> Jenkins: Run Tests
Docker -> Jenkins: Return Build Results
Jenkins -> Developer: Notify Build Status

@enduml
```